# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# MASTER ENV TEMPLATE — references only, NEVER values.
#
# Every line is a 1Password (op-scheme) reference into vault `web-variables`, not a
# secret. Resolve at runtime: `op run --env-file=.env -- <cmd>` or `op inject`.
# Canonical inventory + field labels: credentials-map.md. Rule: secrets-as-references.
#
# THIS IS A MANIFEST, NOT A SINGLE PROCESS ENV. Do NOT resolve every line into one
# process — each surface should take ONLY the lines it needs (least privilege).
# Copy the relevant block into that surface's own .env / connector .env.template.
# New env vars are added here as op-scheme URIs, never literals.
#
# Var names follow naming-discipline (spelled out, no abbrev). Where a consumer
# already reads a specific name, that name is used and noted in a comment.
# Field labels in `web-variables` are NOT always the category default — these match
# credentials-map.md (verified against `op item list`). Confirm before adding new.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────


# ── Bootstrap (NOT op-resolvable — this IS the key that resolves everything else)
# Set directly in each surface's env (shell profile / host secret / Render env /
# GH Actions repo secret), copied from the 1Password item. Never an op-scheme lookup.
OP_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_TOKEN=


# ── GitHub
GITHUB_PAT=op://web-variables/GITHUB_PAT/token
# Least-privilege fine-grained PAT (contents R/W on SchnappAPI/schnapp-os only).
# memory-mcp reads it under the name GITHUB_TOKEN:
GITHUB_TOKEN=op://web-variables/SCHNAPP_OS_PAT/credential


# ── MCP connector bearers (static bearers gating each /mcp origin)
OP_MCP_BEARER=op://web-variables/OP_MCP_BEARER/credential
MEMORY_MCP_BEARER=op://web-variables/MEMORY_MCP_BEARER/credential
MAC_MCP_AUTH_TOKEN=op://web-variables/MAC_MCP_AUTH_TOKEN/credential
GITHUB_MCP_AUTH_TOKEN=op://web-variables/GITHUB_MCP_AUTH_TOKEN/credential


# ── LLM / Anthropic
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=op://web-variables/ANTHROPIC_API_KEY/credential
CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=op://web-variables/CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN/credential


# ── Database (SQL Server in Docker/Colima)
DATABASE_SERVER=op://web-variables/Database/server
DATABASE_NAME=op://web-variables/Database/database
DATABASE_USERNAME=op://web-variables/Database/username
DATABASE_PASSWORD=op://web-variables/Database/password
DATABASE_TRUST_CERT=op://web-variables/Database/trust_cert
MSSQL_SA_PASSWORD=op://web-variables/MSSQL_SA_PASSWORD/credential


# ── Web App (production Next.js) — secrets
ADMIN_PASSCODE=op://web-variables/ADMIN_PASSCODE/credential
ADMIN_REFRESH_CODE=op://web-variables/ADMIN_REFRESH_CODE/credential
AUTH_TOKEN_SECRET=op://web-variables/AUTH_TOKEN_SECRET/credential
